Page explorer (archived)

This file contains the removed "page explorer" navigation that was previously injected into:
- /tevekenysegeink/
- /tevekenysegeink/* service subpages
- /arak.html
- /bemutatkozas.html
- /kapcsolat.html
- /referenciak.html

Status: removed from all pages per request.

---

1) Top-level pages (root) – required CSS include (was added to some pages):

<link rel="stylesheet" href="pages/css/service-subpages.css">

2) Top-level pages (root) – explorer HTML (inserted after the header):

<aside class="service-section-nav" aria-label="Oldal navigáció">
  <nav class="section-nav-tree" aria-label="Sugallat oldalak">
    <a class="section-nav-root-link" href="index.html">Főoldal</a>

    <a class="section-nav-folder-link" href="tevekenysegeink/" data-folder-state="open">Szolgáltatások</a>
    <ul class="section-nav-list" aria-label="Szolgáltatásaink">
      <li class="section-nav-item"><a class="section-nav-link" href="tevekenysegeink/kozbeszerzes-ajanlatkeroknek/">Tanácsadás Ajánlatkérőknek</a></li>
      <li class="section-nav-item"><a class="section-nav-link" href="tevekenysegeink/kozbeszerzes-ajanlattevoknek/">Tanácsadás Ajánlattevőknek</a></li>
      <li class="section-nav-item"><a class="section-nav-link" href="tevekenysegeink/jogorvoslat/">Jogorvoslat</a></li>
      <li class="section-nav-item"><a class="section-nav-link" href="tevekenysegeink/palyazatiras/">Pályázatírás</a></li>
      <li class="section-nav-item"><a class="section-nav-link" href="tevekenysegeink/muszaki-tervezes/">Műszaki ellenőr</a></li>
    </ul>

    <span class="section-nav-folder-link" data-folder-state="open">Sugallat</span>
    <ul class="section-nav-list" aria-label="Sugallat">
      <li class="section-nav-item"><a class="section-nav-link" href="kapcsolat.html">Kapcsolat</a></li>
      <li class="section-nav-item"><a class="section-nav-link" href="arak.html">Áraink</a></li>
      <li class="section-nav-item"><a class="section-nav-link" href="bemutatkozas.html">Rólunk</a></li>
      <li class="section-nav-item"><a class="section-nav-link" href="referenciak.html">Partnereink</a></li>
    </ul>
  </nav>
</aside>

