Explorer styling lived in:
- pages/css/service-subpages.css
  - selectors: .service-section-nav, .section-nav-tree, .section-nav-folder-link, .section-nav-list, .section-nav-link
  - media query: @media (min-width: ...) { .service-section-nav { position: fixed; ... } }


